  3.8101111490104556`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"c2351f77-1103-4cf4-9fe4-\
c8b0823de9d0"],

Cell["\<\
Now that we have gone through a brief review of vectors, we can discuss their \
application to the concept of angular momentum. \
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.8100556995857887`*^9, 3.8100557432002*^9}, {
   3.8101094362577724`*^9, 3.8101095163760753`*^9}, 
   3.8101096658101816`*^9},ExpressionUUID->"5c4deed1-320e-489b-a063-\
a970de98affe"],

Cell["\<\
For linear motion of a particle, we have a linear momentum given by\
\>", "Text",
