  3.810109574197364*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"1b3fc27c-1ffe-423d-8499-\
88572d6ce29d"],

Cell[TextData[{
 "where",
 StyleBox[" r",
  FontWeight->"Bold",
  FontSlant->"Italic"],
 " is the position vector giving the distance and direction from a fixed \
point. In analogy with equation (30), we can also write out the angular \
momentum as"
}], "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.810109569726921*^9, 3.8101096458457084`*^9}, {
  3.810109703295032*^9, 3.810109730468155*^9}, {3.810109884914685*^9, 
